ing: 1 head romaine lettuce- rinsed, dried and chopped
1/2 cup cucumber - peeled, seeded and chopped
des: "This recipe is perfect for families who like flavorful and easy salads!  Toss with your favorite salad dressing."
ins: In a large salad bowl, combine the Romaine, cheese, green onion, cucumber, carrot, oregano, poultry seasoning and celery. Add enough salad dressing to coat, toss and serve.
